name: EndNote Import File
summary: Learn about .ENW files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: More recent versions of EndNote export EndNote libraries (.ENL files) in the .TXT, .RTF, .HTM, and .XML formats rather than the ENW format. However, EndNote can still import ENW files. You can also share libraries using archived EndNote libraries (.ENLX files).
NOTE: Clarivate EndNote was previously developed by Thomson Reuters.
